            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De miseria et miseris</head>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e114">
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>¶ De miseria et miseris. Rubrica. 8.
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e119">
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e116">IOb <sic>Hystoria</sic>. capitulo 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e123">Deus ponit humi
        <lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>les in sublime: et mentes
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>erigit sospitate.</quote> 
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e131"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e128">36. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e133">Quidam ami
        <lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no"/>cus Iob nomine eliu in consolatione. Iob dixit
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>ei: Caue ne declines ad iniquitatem. Hanc enim
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>cepisti sequi post miseriam.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e141">
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e145">Salomon in prouerbiis. capitulo 19.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e147">Homo in
        <lb ed="#V" n="19" break="no"/>digens misericors est.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e148">
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e157">Salustius in iugurtino:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e152">Expertus sum pa
        <lb ed="#V" n="21" break="no"/>rum fidei miseris esse.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e158">
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e169">Tullius paradoxorum distinctione. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e162">Ut improbo et stul
        <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>to et inerti nemini bene esse potest: Sic bonus vir
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>et fortis et sapiens miser esse non potest.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e170">
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e183">Ouidius de ponto. libro 2. epistola 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e174">Res timida est
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>omnis miser.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e180"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e193">Libro. 4. et finali. epistola 4.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e182">Nil adeo fortuna grauis miserabile fecit:
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>Ut muniant nulla gaudia per te malum.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e190">
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e207">Epistola. 12.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e194">Crede mihi miseros prudentia summa reliquit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>Et sensus cum re consiliumque fugit.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e202">
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e222">Idem de nuce.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="33"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e206">Quam miserum est odium damnis accedere nostris.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e213">
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e234">Quintilianus declamationum. i. declamatione.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e217">Semper si
        <lb ed="#V" n="35" break="no"/>bi custodiunt minseri: ne esse miserabiles desi
        <lb ed="#V" n="36" break="no"/>nant.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e225"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e246">13. declamatione.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e227">Leuior est calamitas cui
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>blanditur aliquid de voluptate letitia.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e233">
        <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>¶ <ref><!--add xml tag-->Seneca tragediarum in thieste. capitulo 11.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e237">Proprium hoc miseros sequitur vicium.
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>Nunquam rebus crede letis.
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>Redere felix fortuna licet.
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>Tamen afflictos gaudere piget.
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>Flendi miseris dira cupido est.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e251">
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e276">In troa. capitulo 12. et penultimo.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e255">Nemo se credit miserum: sit licet. <!--321.xml-->
          <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
        <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>Tolle felices.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e267">
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e294">Idem epistolarum ad lucillum. libro 9. epistola i.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e271">Nemo nisi vicio miser est.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e277">
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e307">Idem declamationum. libro 8. capitulo i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e281">Fortuna quos mise
        <lb ed="#V" n="50" break="no"/>ros facit etiam superstitiosos facit.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e288">
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e319">Lucanus. libro 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e292">Seruat multos fortuma nocen
        <lb ed="#V" n="52" break="no"/>tes. Et tantum miseris irasci numina possunt.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e298">
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e331">Statius <sic>thebaydos</sic> libro 11.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e302">Hic miseris fu
        <lb ed="#V" n="54" break="no"/>ror est: astare periculo. Nec librare metus: et tu
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>ta odisse. Quid causus iuuat ostentare pudentes</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e310">
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e345">Libro 12</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e314">Amant miseri lamenta: malisque fruuntur.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e318">
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e355">Fulgentius. libro i. fabula i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e322">Sola est medicina
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>minseriarum obliuio.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e328">
        <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e367">Boetius de consolatione. libro i. capitulo 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e332">Hic etiam ve
        <lb ed="#V" n="60" break="no"/>stris cumulis malis accedit: quod existimatio
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>plurimorum non rerum merita: sed fortune spectat euen
        <lb ed="#V" n="62" break="no"/>tum. eaque tantum iudicat esse prouisa qui felicitas commen
        <lb ed="#V" n="63" break="no"/>dauerit. Quo fit vt existimatio bona prima omni
        <lb ed="#V" n="64" break="no"/>um deserat infelices. Hoc tantum dixerim vltimam
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>esse aduerse fortune sarcinam: quod dum mise
        <lb ed="#V" n="66" break="no"/>ris aliquod crimen affigitur que proferuntur
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>meruisse redduntur.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e353">
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e395">Cassiodorus epistolarum libro 5. epistola 29.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e357">Necesse est
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>vt amplius permoueat visa quam audita calami
        <lb ed="#V" n="70" break="no"/>tas.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e366"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e407">36. epistola.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e368">Non est ignauie culpa quam excusat
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>miseranda calamitas.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e374"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e417">Libro 10. epistola i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e376">Deus consue
        <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>uit casus asperos in prospera commutare.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e382">
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e429">Auctor libelli qui dicitur pamphylus. capitulo 18.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e386">Parua
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>nocent miseris: miseros mala multa sequuntur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>Spesque laborque suus remanent in dubio.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e394">
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e443">Gualterius de castellione. libro 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e398">Sors mise
        <lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>ri querula est.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e404">
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e455">Iacobus beneuentanus. capitulo 52.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e408">Ludibrium
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>populo fit miser omnis homo.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e414">
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e468">Prouerbia metricum extraordinem librorum vagantia.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e418">Solati
        <lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>um est miseris socios habere penarum.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-d1e425">
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Rd1e480">Prouerbia vulgaria.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e08143-Qd1e429">Ai cham magri vale mosche.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
